Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:29.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}走り出せば　なびく髪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:35.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}澄んだ空を　呼んでくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:42.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}行き先なら　もう決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}握るたづな　熱くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}迷いを打ち消して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}心動かすのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:01.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}いつでも君なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}信じてみたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:08.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}出会いがまたひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:13.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}明日をかえてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:21.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}願い溢れる度に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:26.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}ふわり風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:32.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}新しいページ　めくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:39.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}誰も知らないのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:44.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}一緒に見つけたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:54.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}君が描く未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:29.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}伴随跑动的步伐 头发随风飘动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:35.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}唤来一片清澈的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:42.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}旅途的终点 早已决定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}手中紧握的缰绳 变得炙热
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}打消一切的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}触动我心扉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:01.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}总是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}我开始变得想要去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:08.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}还有下一次相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:13.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}将明天重新谱写
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:21.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}每当愿望充满心田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:26.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}便会扬起轻盈柔风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:32.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}翻过那故事的下一页
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:39.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}如果我们谁都未曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:44.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}那就让我们一同去找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:54.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}你所描绘的未来
